A "hosting domain" (as opposed to ["sending domain"](/glossary-sending-domain)) is a custom domain (like yourname.com) which you use to host your Buttondown subscribe pages and/or archives.

Looking to figure out how to set up a hosting domain? Check out our [guide](/hosting-on-a-custom-domain).